     H            Y.
     F** UTLR50A ************************************************
     F*  UTILITY : CHECK NUMERIC                                *
     F*  WRITTEN : JW (SRA)  2023.05.17                         *
     F*  FUNCTION: CHECK ALL NUMERIC OR NOT                     *
     F*---------------------------------------------------------*
     F*  CALLING SEQ.
     F*                    CALL 'UTLR50A'
     F*                    PARM           $LTR   20
     F*                    PARM           $RSLT   1
     F*   IN  $LTR   20A LETERS TO BE CHECKED
     F*   OUT $RSLT   1A Y: ALL NUMERIC, N= NOT ALL NUMERIC
     F******************************************************
     E                    VAL     1   1 10
     E                    TBL        10  1
     E                    DAT        20  1
      *--------------------------------------------------------
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           $LTR   20
     C                     PARM           $RSLT   1
      *
     C                     MOVEAVAL,1     TBL
     C                     MOVEA$LTR      DAT
     C                     MOVE 'NG'      OKFLG   2
      * LENGTH
     C                     Z-ADD11        IX
     C                     DO   *HIVAL
     C                     SUB  1         IX
     C           IX        IFEQ 0
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           DAT,IX    IFNE *BLANK
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C                     Z-ADDIX        @LNG    20
      *
     C           @LNG      IFLT 1
     C           @LNG      ORGT 20
     C                     GOTO ENDP
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C           1         DO   @LNG      IX      20
     C                     MOVE 'NG'      OKFLG
      *
     C           1         DO   10        IY      20
     C           TBL,IY    IFEQ DAT,IX
     C                     MOVE 'OK'      OKFLG
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           OKFLG     IFEQ 'NG'
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     ENDDO
      *
     C           ENDP      TAG
     C           OKFLG     IFEQ 'OK'
     C                     MOVE 'Y'       $RSLT
     C                     ELSE
     C                     MOVE 'N'       $RSLT
     C                     ENDIF
      *
     C                     MOVE *ON       *INLR
     C                     RETRN
** VAL
0123456789
